                     ComponentName cmp)
              throws NameNotFoundException
        Build codec infos based on a component name of a manifest It will retrieve SipManager.META_LIB_NAME and SipManager.META_LIB_INIT_FACTORY from the meta datas of the component
        参数:
        ctxt - The current application context
        cmp - The component name of the remote plugin application

        NameNotFoundException - If the remote component is not found
